summary: Quick dungeon I made to familiarize myself with creation kit.
descriptionHtml:
This is a quick dungeon I made to familiarize myself with the creation kit, the navmesh is a little messed up so don't count on enemies/companions to follow you and the dungeon itself is very small due to the nature of this undertaking (learning).Â 

The dungeon can be found next to riverwood over the bridge and to the left or by simply typing coc daandein into the console.
author: Kallum260
